repository.name: e-commerce-smartcarthub-microservices
repository.description: This is a simple e-commerce application built using microservices architecture. The application is designed to manage user profiles, products, orders, and related functionalities. Each microservice corresponds to a specific domain, facilitating modular development and scalability.
